dct_description_sm: drawn and published by David H. Burr.
Relief shown by hachures and pictorially.
Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
2 bar scales on map given in "English Miles" and "British statute miles".
Shows topography, drainage, boundaries, places of historical interest, boundaries of the Tribes of Israel.
